Add/remove server in the address book 
For your convenience you can bookmark a server in your address book. 
These servers will be always in the list (they are marked yellow). 
Add server to the address book: pressing the "Add/remove" button 
calls up the window to enter/edit the server address. In case one of the 
active servers has been selected from the list at the moment, its address 
will appear in the window. 
Remove server: choose a server from the address book and press the
"add/remove" button.
